These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, biathlon, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | snowboarding | biathlon | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, pepper, kiwi
1. the person eating pepper is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | avocado | kiwi | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | sudoku | gardening | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, house, trance
1. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | trance | house |

